org.rdkit.knime.internals

Class StreamingOperatorInternalsBag

  • java.lang.Object
    • StreamableOperatorInternals
      • org.rdkit.knime.internals.StreamingOperatorInternalsBag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RDKitInternals<StreamingOperatorInternalsBag>

    public class StreamingOperatorInternalsBag
extends StreamableOperatorInternals
implements RDKitInternals<StreamingOperatorInternalsBag>
    This class acts as a bag to make it possible to handle multiple internals objects together. They need to be named when put into this bag and will be accessed by their names again. All of them are required to implement the interface RDKitInternals which defines methods to load and save the state of these objects.
    Author:
    Manuel Schwarze
